{"tid":1928301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北歐航空大解9成員工 霸氣女總理：政府付75%薪水","createTime":"2020-03-16T10:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T10:24:59.000Z","uid":21141,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff0181265c2488a73140beba1d6c161c6bbe513a","tid":1928301,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:03:02.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎（俗稱武漢肺炎）使全球人心惶惶，航空業屢受重創，北歐航空（SAS）15日宣佈臨時裁減9成員工，約1萬人受影響，丹麥總理佛瑞德里克森(Mette Frederiksen)當日亦宣佈，為減緩裁員潮，政府將會負擔員工75%薪水。<br />\n<br />\n北歐航空是丹麥、挪威及瑞典3國的國家航空公司，由於近期飽受疫情打擊，民眾外出旅遊意慾降低，以及多國發出旅遊警示，北歐航空執行長Rickard Gustafson表示，目前已經沒有進出北歐斯堪地那維亞半島的航班需求，因此公司自16日起會暫停大部份業務，以及大幅減少航班數量。<br />\n<br />\n至於被裁減的航班什麼時候復航，北歐航空指出，要直至受重創的商用航空環境得到改善。另外，北歐航空也宣佈，將裁撤公司1萬名員工，即佔總員工數的90%。<br />\n<br />\n面對疫情引起經濟不景氣，從而導致的裁員潮，丹麥總理佛瑞德里克森(Mette Frederiksen)於15日在哥本哈根的簡報會上宣佈，倘若私人公司不得不裁員至少30%員工或是多達50人，可向政府申請補助，政府將補助每名員工的75%薪水，補助金額以丹麥克朗23,000元（約台幣10萬多元）為上限，此方案將回溯到3月9日，實行至6月9日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-03-16/376110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-03-16%2F376110&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=13450818\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-03-16/376110</a><br />\n<br />\n裁撚左九成人都唔執，勁過廚叉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979166c1fef388a65809b12de8f4e501e4264785","tid":1928301,"uid":21141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"呢個補貼出現係香港<br />\n班無良奸商會唔會瘋狂裁員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5411b4dd80986212d290fabb0bfd8703d3a19424","tid":1928301,"uid":8014,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"渣ga<br />\n<br />\n我地香港公務員啱啱先通過加薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n逆市全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5aa65ab9993a284f263db1ca9a721167833748","tid":1928301,"uid":33433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:07:39.000Z","msg":"係咪Flag carrier嚟 正常都好難執 政府一定救"},{"pid":"f80836e25fde8d88c2c2afb3ec6bb95333dd3333","tid":1928301,"uid":21141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5411b4dd80986212d290fabb0bfd8703d3a19424","tid":1928301,"uid":8014,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"渣ga<br />\n<br />\n我地香港公務員啱啱先通過加薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n逆市全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:10:23.000Z","msg":"全球經濟插水，財政赤字都加薪<br />\n香港共產黨世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f88acabc5127f989a8694f821f479d1729d604","tid":1928301,"uid":176728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:12:03.000Z","msg":"大解...諗起痾屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692d2663fbb4584efed72689b9547d4b61e03558","tid":1928301,"uid":65604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:12:13.000Z","msg":"北歐航空有得大解，咁小解呢？"},{"pid":"6e7e49ecf691989ade729adeee2f5fec26b96050","tid":1928301,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"692d2663fbb4584efed72689b9547d4b61e03558","tid":1928301,"uid":65604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:12:13.000Z","msg":"北歐航空有得大解，咁小解呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:13:34.000Z","msg":"厨叉算唔算小解"},{"pid":"c9b474ec0530523ceb1dca457567a1db771ae522","tid":1928301,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5aa65ab9993a284f263db1ca9a72